'''马尔代夫'''对游客实行落地签证，外国人前往马尔代夫旅游时，一般可免费获得最长不超过30天的落地签证。<ref name=doi>{{cite web|title=Tourist Visa|url=https://immigration.gov.mv/tourist-visa/|publisher=Maldives Immigration, Republic of Maldives}}</ref>

哈萨克斯坦国民可免签证在马尔代夫逗留30天<ref>[https://www.gov.mv/en/news-and-communications/maldives-and-kazakhstan-sign-visa-waiver-agreement#:~:text=The%20Government%20of%20Maldives%20and,nationals%2C%20for%20a%20period%20of Maldives and Kazakhstan Sign Visa Waiver Agreement]</ref>，印度<ref>[http://foreign.gov.mv/images/consular/Visa%20FAQ%20(India%20and%20Maldives)%20(1)%20(1).pdf FAQs for Maldivians and Indians travelling to either country]</ref>和俄罗斯<ref>[https://foreign.gov.mv/index.php/en/mediacentre/news/5081-government-of-maldives-and-government-of-the-russian-federation-sign-an-agreement-on-mutual-exemption-of-visa-requirements Government of Maldives and Government of the Russian Federation sign an Agreement on Mutual Exemption of Visa requirements.]</ref>的国民可免签证在马尔代夫逗留90天。

==入境要求==
所有来到马尔代夫的访客必须：

* 持有剩余至少1个月有效期的[[可機讀護照|可機讀护照或旅行证件]]<ref name="EntryRequirements">{{cite web|title=Entry Requirements|url=https://immigration.gov.mv/tourist-visa/}}</ref>
* 已预付的酒店预定单<ref name="EntryRequirements"/>
* 有足够的资金用于在马尔代夫逗留的时间<ref name="EntryRequirements"/>
* 持有已确认前往/返回本国或居住国的机票（不适用于有效居留证持有人）<ref name="EntryRequirements"/>
* 持有前往下一个目的地的入境文件（如签证）<ref name="EntryRequirements"/>
* 所有往返于马尔代夫的旅行在航班起飞前72小时内填写并提交[https://immigration.gov.mv/immigration-introduces-electronic-traveller-health-declaration/ 旅客声明]，该表格必须以电子方式通过[http://imuga.immigration.gov.mv/ IMUGA]提交<ref name="EntryRequirements"/>
* 持有黄热病疫苗接种证书，如果来自[https://immigration.gov.mv/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/YELLOW-FEVER-COUNTRIES-2.pdf 黄热病流行国家]<ref name="EntryRequirements"/>

